<section class="unification-timeline">
    <h2>Historical Steps Toward Unity</h2>
    
    <div class="spinoza-section">
        <h3>Spinoza's Monism</h3>
        <div class="portrait-container">
            <img 
                src="https://oclesis.com.mx/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/spinoza-e1516702848503.jpg"
                alt="Baruch Spinoza portrait"
                class="spinoza-portrait"
            />
        </div>
        <div class="concept-animation">
            <div class="unity-symbol"></div>
            <div class="manifestations"></div>
        </div>
        <p>
            Baruch Spinoza argued that all of existence is one substance (God or Nature), 
            and everything we perceive as distinct is simply an expression of this singular entity.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-grid">
        <div class="timeline-card newton">
            <h3>Newton's Universal Laws</h3>
            <div class="formula">F = G(m₁m₂)/r²</div>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="celestial-body planet"></div>
                <div class="orbit-path"></div>
                <div class="celestial-body sun"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                Newton unified terrestrial and celestial mechanics, showing that the same 
                laws govern falling apples and orbiting planets.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-card maxwell">
            <h3>Maxwell's Electromagnetism</h3>
            <div class="formula">∇ × E = -∂B/∂t</div>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="em-field">
                    <div class="electric-field"></div>
                    <div class="magnetic-field"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>
                James Clerk Maxwell unified electricity and magnetism, revealing them as 
                aspects of a single electromagnetic force.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-card einstein">
            <h3>Einstein's Relativity</h3>
            <div class="formula">E = mc²</div>
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="spacetime-grid"></div>
                <div class="mass-object"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                Einstein unified space and time into spacetime, and showed that mass and 
                energy are interchangeable aspects of a single entity.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .unification-timeline {
        margin: 4rem 0;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    h2, h3 {
        text-align: center;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .spinoza-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .portrait-container {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(var(--accent), 0.3), rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3));
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .portrait-container:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .spinoza-portrait {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 4px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3);
    }

    .timeline-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .timeline-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-dark), 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2);
    }

    .formula {
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    }

    .animation-container {
        height: 150px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .celestial-body {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .sun {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent));
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    .planet {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        animation: orbit 4s infinite linear;
    }

    .orbit-path {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.3);
        border-radius: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    .em-field {
        position: relative;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .electric-field, .magnetic-field {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        top: 50%;
        transform-origin: center;
        animation: wavePropagate 3s infinite;
    }

    .magnetic-field {
        transform: rotate(90deg);
        background: rgb(var(--accent));
        animation-delay: 0.75s;
    }

    .spacetime-grid {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2) 1px, transparent 1px),
                          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 20px 20px;
        animation: gridDistort 4s infinite;
    }

    .mass-object {
        position: absolute;
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent));
        border-radius: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    .concept-animation {
        height: 200px;
        position: relative;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .unity-symbol {
        position: absolute;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        animation: pulsate 4s infinite;
    }

    .manifestations {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at center,
            rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        animation: expand 6s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes orbit {
        from { transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(50px) rotate(0deg); }
        to { transform: rotate(360deg) translateX(50px) rotate(-360deg); }
    }

    @keyframes wavePropagate {
        0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
        100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
    }

    @keyframes gridDistort {
        0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
        50% { transform: scale(0.8) rotate(5deg); }
    }

    @keyframes pulsate {
        0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }
        50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.2); opacity: 0.4; }
    }

    @keyframes expand {
        0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.2; }
        50% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0.4; }
    }
</style>